{
  "id": "adv_event_2603_01_05_01",
  "title": "大切な人への\n曲",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――合宿終了後の朝",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "endTime": 1.3666665952,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mnaroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "mnaroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu Narumiya",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_05-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "昨日、帰ってからはあっという間でしたわね\n悩んでいたのがウソみたいに曲もすぐ完成しましたし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2.2666665952,
      "endTime": 11.0808612745,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 16400.890241999998
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mnaroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "mnaroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 11.2975274325
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu Narumiya",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_05-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "感傷に浸っていたいところですが、急ぎましょうか\nそろそろ電車の時間ですし、先に出てますわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.2975274325,
      "endTime": 20.0610646487,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 11780.2041451
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mnaroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "mnaroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 20.2443981727
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_05-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "待って、せっかくだし途中まで――\nあ、ペンダントが……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20.2443981727,
      "endTime": 25.9443982442,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mnaroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "mnaroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 23.0777315776
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mnaroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "mnaroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 26.1735820691
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_05-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "（どうしよう、お姉ちゃんの鞄の中に落ちちゃった……）\n（それにこの鞄は……お姉ちゃんがあの日持っていた物）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.1735820691,
      "endTime": 39.016960899,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 20837.482841799996
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_05-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "人の鞄の中に手を入れるのは気が引けるけど……\nごめんね、お姉ちゃん。ちょっとだけ失礼します……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.2002944231,
      "endTime": 49.752493596,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 10735.532697000004
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mnaroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "mnaroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 44.4443982442
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mnaroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "mnaroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 49.9358271201
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_05-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "えーっと……あった！　良かったぁ……\nあれ？　もしかして、鞄に入ってるこの袋って……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.9358271201,
      "endTime": 64.0358273108,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 14283.333714799994
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mnaroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "mnaroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 64.2191608349
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_05-ktn005.m4a",
      "text": "（やっぱり……お姉ちゃんのペンダントが入ってる）\n（そっか。ずっと、ここにあったんだね）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64.2191608349,
      "endTime": 76.9191604534,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mnaroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "mnaroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 77.1024939774
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_05-ktn006.m4a",
      "text": "（すずが、お姉ちゃんもこのペンダントを通して、私の）\n（ことをいつも想っていたんじゃないかって言ってたけど）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.1024939774,
      "endTime": 85.5926757095,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mnaroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "mnaroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 85.7760092336
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_05-ktn007.m4a",
      "text": "（NEXT VENUSグランプリの決勝戦の日も……）\n（ううん、ずっと……ずっと……お姉ちゃんは私のことを）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.7760092336,
      "endTime": 100.5258736211,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mnaroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "mnaroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 100.7092071452
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_05-ktn008.m4a",
      "text": "私、お姉ちゃんの、支えになれてたんだね……\nうう、ぐすっ、お姉ちゃん……お姉ちゃん……！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 100.7092071452,
      "endTime": 115.8369172969,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 15457.458822100009
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mnaroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "mnaroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 116.0202508209
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu Narumiya",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_05-suz003.m4a",
      "text": "もう、遅いですわよ！　急がないと……\nって、どうして泣いてるんですの！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 116.0202508209,
      "endTime": 123.89190847859999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mnaroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "mnaroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 120.8666659673
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mnaroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "mnaroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 124.0752420026
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_05-ktn009.m4a",
      "text": "うわぁ～～～ん……すず……ぐすっ……私……\nお姉ちゃんのことが……お姉ちゃんのことが大好き……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 124.0752420026,
      "endTime": 140.71496940420002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mnaroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "mnaroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 140.8983029284
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu Narumiya",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_05-suz005.m4a",
      "text": "もう、無理に喋らなくていいですわよ。よしよし……\n麻奈様も琴乃のことが大好きに決まってますわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 140.8983029284,
      "endTime": 152.4168974795,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――月のテンペストバレンタインライブ当日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 153.3335653541,
      "endTime": 155.10023819589998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 155.1002381959
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko Saeki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_05-hrk001.m4a",
      "text": "招待してくれてありがとう、琴乃ちゃん。今回の新曲は\n渚ちゃんがセンターなのよね。ふふ、楽しみだわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 156.0335714577,
      "endTime": 166.7835712669,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 159.8173761551
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 166.966904791
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_05-ktn010.m4a",
      "text": "期待してて下さい。今日のために\nメンバー一丸となって仕上げてきましたから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 166.966904791,
      "endTime": 172.982029398,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 173.1653629222
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura Kawasaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_05-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "もしかして私達もやった告白大会を月ストもやるの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 173.1653629222,
      "endTime": 178.66536273149998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 178.8486962555
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_05-ktn011.m4a",
      "text": "え、ええと、それは……\nライブ本番のお楽しみということで",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 178.8486962555,
      "endTime": 188.3971312759,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 188.5804647999
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio Kanzaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_05-rio001.m4a",
      "text": "暗にやるって言ってるようなものじゃない\nけど、どうしたの？　本番前の楽屋に呼び出すなんて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 188.5804647999,
      "endTime": 195.8567912655,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 196.0401247896
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio Kanzaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_05-rio002.m4a",
      "text": "ま、まさか私達もそれに付き合わせるつもりじゃ……\n先に断っておくけれど、絶対にやらないわよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 196.0401247896,
      "endTime": 205.2746827043,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 205.4580162283
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_05-ktn012.m4a",
      "text": "ち、違います。みなさんに来ていただいたのは\n私のソロライブツアーのことで、お願いがあるからです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 205.4580162283,
      "endTime": 214.6543203588,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 208.3679841678
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 214.8376538829
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
